  <brief_title>Non-contrast 3D MR Angiography for Assessment of the Thoracic Aorta in Pregnancy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Native High-resolution 3D SSFP MR Angiography for Assessment of the Thoracic Aorta in Pregnant Subjects With Familial Aortopathies</official_title>
  <sponsors>
